      		<paragraph>The following example deletes the attachment named <code>sample_attachment</code> for the design document with the identifier <code>_design/beer4</code>.
      		</paragraph>
      		<paragraph>
      			<strong>Request</strong>
      		</paragraph>
      		<code-block>
DELETE  /beer-db/_design/beer4?rev=1-2ed3e22a2f64b5364028e5b5842fcf41 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:4984

</code-block>
